A New Perspective on Biometrics & Identity



Driven by massive growth in mobile commerce, digital identity and globalization, as well as rapidly evolving security threats, the identity and biometrics market is taking off and going mainstream.
With its team, technology platform, and global partnerships, Tascent™ is changing the landscape of biometrics and identity. We are a Silicon Valley-based company with a world view: Develop products that are easy to use, create scalable and flexible platforms, and provide focused attention on supporting our customers.
With a combination of iris recognition and other biometric technologies in high throughput and mobile environments, Tascent provides secure biometric identity to tens of millions of people every year.



   


