Tascent M6
Redefining possible in mobile biometrics




Access Data SheetDownload Data Sheet
Watch the Video






Tascent M6 leverages the Apple iPhone to deliver new levels of performance and usability to form factors previously unimaginable in biometric identity. It combines iris, face, fingerprint, and voice biometrics in a sophisticated open architecture approach that allows partners to rapidly create and deploy powerful custom apps.
[ Learn More ]


   



   


Applications

   

 Travel Tascent’s high throughput and mobile identity products deliver efficiency, safety, and personalized treatment for the wide range of use cases consistently encountered in air travel, from bag drop to VIP lounge to boarding and even in-flight.
Learn more


 Border Management Tascent’s iris recognition and multimodal biometric systems enable increased efficiency and decreased queues in high throughput border management environments while also supporting mobile applications in the air, on the ground, and in the field.Learn more


 Public Safety Positive identity confirmation using Tascent’s multimodal high throughput and smartphone-based mobile biometric capabilities is helping to improve the safety, security, and efficiency of public safety organizations around the world.Learn more

   



  








